== Amavuka. ==
Valentine Sendanyoye Rugwabiza wavutse taliki 25 Nyakanga 1963 Rugwabiza Umunyarwandakazi umunyapolitiki uhagarariye uRwanda mu muryango wibihugu byunz'ubumwe kuva muri 2016( united nations).<ref>https://www.un.org/press/en/2022/sga2101.doc.htm</ref>

== Ubwene gihugu. ==
Rwanda.

== Umwuga. ==
Ubucuruzi bwumwuga.<ref>https://www.un.org/press/en/2022/sga2101.doc.htm</ref>

== Icyo Akora. ==
Ahagarariye uRwanda bihorano muri United Notion.<ref>https://www.weforum.org/people/valentine-rugwabiza</ref>

== Ubuzima Bwite. ==
Valentine Sendanyoye Rugwabiza washakanye na John Paulin Sendanyoye.

Amashuri.

Rugwabiza wabonye impanya bushobozi yo kiciro cya Mbere ni cyakabiri cya kaminuza mu bijyanye nubukungu yavanye muri kaminuza nkuru ya zayire (National University of Zaire).

== Ubumenyi mundimi. ==
Valentine Sendanyoye Rugwabiza Umunyarwandakazi uvuga indimi Enye arizo Ikinyarwanda, Igiswahili, Icyongereza ni Gifaransa.<ref>https://minusca.unmissions.org/en/secretary-general-appoints-ms-valentine-rugwabiza-rwanda-special-representative-central-african-0</ref>

== Urugendo Mu miyoborero. ==
Rugwabiza kuva 2005 kugeza 2013 Yari umuyobozi wikigo cy'isi mubucurizi world trade organization (WTO).

